\f1\fs28 \cf3 \cb4 \strokec3 For new parents we follow the recommendations of the American Academy of Pediatric Dentistry \'96 "first visit by the first birthday". Recognizing the short attention span of 1 year olds, we will perform an exam, demonstrate proper oral hygiene techniques, and discuss your child's eating, feeding, and oral habits with you.\
